	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sperabam omnino fratres hos mecum pransuros; sic enim licuisset prolixius scribere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc hoc solum ad te, quod <placeName ref="l1048">Brandenburgensis</placeName> domus cum Caesare agit sciscitata, num eius autoritate proscriptus <persName ref="p8371">Albertus</persName> sit et num idem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538">Cesar</persName> punire constituat <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20318">H[einricum] Brunsvicensem</persName>, quod contra pacis legem 32 ordines imperii vexarit bello; id enim si ipse non faciat, se esse curaturos ut fiat.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Conscribit militem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20318">Heinrichus</persName>, sed non potest in unum colligere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Conveniunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1048">Brandenburg[ens</placeName> s], <placeName ref="l749">Saxoniae</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l213">Hassiae</placeName> principes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l337">Neoburgi</placeName>, ut veterem inter se confoderationem renovent, inter se et alia tractaturi.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18">Augustae</placeName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18477">Ferdinandus</persName> cum sacrificis urgeat <foreign xml:lang="de">den lantfriden zuͦ <placeName ref="l157">Franckfurt</placeName></foreign> idem vellet et Caesar obtinere.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Contra vero electores <placeName ref="l749">Saxoniae</placeName>, <placeName ref="l1048">Brandenburgensis</placeName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3590">Palatinus</persName> cum aliis compluribus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1204">Pataviensia</placeName> pacta, quae nisi procedant, aliam consiliorum suorum rationem inituros profitentur.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque male sibi metuunt pfaffi, eo quod pactis iis libera religionis professio aperte concedatur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogemus dominum, ut suorum animos augeat et confirmet et nos misericorditer tueatur a malo.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale in domino, mi <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Bullingere</persName> venerande, et <persName ref="p3099">Sulcerum</persName> perge amare et precibus iuvare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28">Basileae</placeName> ultima marcii anno 1555.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3099">Sulcerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro praestantissimo d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, domino et fratri colendissimo suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
